{"text_id":41291,"tokens":["In"," this"," study",","," we"," report"," on"," the"," observation"," of"," simultaneous"," magnetic"," order"," and"," large"," electric"," polarization"," at"," room"," temperature"," in"," Bi","Fe","O","3"," single"," crystals","."," The"," coexistence"," of"," magnetic"," and"," ferro","electric"," ordering"," in"," multi","ferro","ics"," such"," as"," Bi","Fe","O","3"," is"," of"," great"," interest"," for"," the"," development"," of"," advanced"," electronic"," devices","."," However",","," achieving"," such"," coexistence"," at"," room"," temperature"," remains"," a"," significant"," challenge",".","Through"," a"," combination"," of"," X","-","ray"," diffraction",","," magnetic"," measurements",","," and"," polarization"," measurements",","," we"," have"," shown"," that"," Bi","Fe","O","3"," single"," crystals"," indeed"," display"," both"," magnetic"," and"," ferro","electric"," ordering"," at"," room"," temperature","."," The"," observed"," magnetic"," order"," originates"," from"," anti","ferro","magnetic"," coupling"," between"," the"," Fe"," ions",","," while"," the"," large"," electric"," polarization"," is"," due"," to"," the"," displacement"," of"," Bi"," ions"," from"," their"," center"," positions",".","Our"," work"," provides"," insight"," into"," the"," physical"," mechanisms"," that"," underlie"," the"," simultaneous"," coexistence"," of"," magnetic"," and"," ferro","electric"," ordering"," in"," Bi","Fe","O","3"," single"," crystals","."," Our"," findings"," have"," significant"," implications"," for"," the"," design"," and"," development"," of"," novel"," multi","ferro","ic"," electronic"," devices",","," such"," as"," magnetic"," sensors"," and"," electrically"," controllable"," memories","."," These"," results"," demonstrate"," the"," potential"," of"," Bi","Fe","O","3"," as"," a"," promising"," material"," for"," the"," development"," of"," multifunctional"," electronic"," devices","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","mode